01:03:36.580 --> 01:03:45.640
say, this function of H with
H, what do I have to do?

01:03:45.640 --> 01:03:50.590
I have to do a sum over
alpha d rho with respect

01:03:50.590 --> 01:03:55.510
to, let's say-- actually,
