01:13:27.860 --> 01:13:28.360
Right?

01:13:28.360 --> 01:13:29.500
PROFESSOR: Observables?

01:13:29.500 --> 01:13:30.530
No.

01:13:30.530 --> 01:13:36.000
I mean, here, if
